overview: Two best friends who flunked out of their freshman year of college decide to give higher education one more try. The only problem is neither of them is actually enrolled. They attend classes at the university, spark chaos and navigate college life while spending their nights in the school's library. However as one thing leads to another their cover may be blown, but they will stop at nothing to reach their dreams of being the crazy fun college students they've sought out to be. Literally nothing...
tagline: What are you talking about? Of course we go here...
title: Gaslight University
